WEBVTT

01:38.160 --> 01:40.560
EPISODE 1

01:50.680 --> 01:54.160
JINLING CITY

02:33.240 --> 02:34.840
Luwei Weiwei, be careful!

02:35.560 --> 02:37.480
Zhenshui, I'll hold him off.

02:37.560 --> 02:39.200
You attack him, as usual.

02:39.280 --> 02:40.160
Sure.

03:56.920 --> 03:57.880
Hurry, catch up!

04:14.520 --> 04:17.000
Amazing! It's a Mage Class OP Necklace!

04:17.079 --> 04:18.959
Nini, it's your equipment.

04:19.360 --> 04:22.640
Wow! I'm so lucky today!

04:22.720 --> 04:23.880
A Mage Class OP Necklace?

04:25.800 --> 04:27.480
Luwei Weiwei, do you want to duke it out?

04:29.160 --> 04:30.040
Sure.

04:30.280 --> 04:32.440
There should be stakes involved, no?

04:32.920 --> 04:35.880
Let's bet on the necklace boss dropped.
What do you say?

04:37.440 --> 04:39.600
I see, you want the necklace.

04:40.280 --> 04:41.600
But it's not my equipment.

04:42.680 --> 04:43.720
I'll play you, then.

04:45.680 --> 04:49.080
You're a top-10 clan leader!
I have zero chance against you.

04:49.680 --> 04:52.120
You can ask Luwei Weiwei to fight for you.

04:52.200 --> 04:54.560
If I lose, I'll give you
a Mage Class OP Ring.

04:55.120 --> 04:56.160
Are you scared?

04:56.960 --> 04:57.880
Weiwei?

05:01.240 --> 05:03.120
- Sure.
- Good.

05:03.200 --> 05:05.760
Five o'clock,
by the lodge outside Jinling City.

05:13.120 --> 05:16.960
What did you want to talk about, Zhenshui?
Are there monsters to defeat here?

05:19.720 --> 05:22.800
Weiwei, we've become in-game spouses
for more than half a year.

05:22.880 --> 05:26.720
Isn't it awkward
that you're still calling me Zhenshui?

05:30.000 --> 05:32.960
Wouldn't it be more awkward
if I called you Wuxiang?

05:33.040 --> 05:36.040
Hubby, today's mission
is 12 three-eyed monkeys.

05:36.120 --> 05:38.520
- Won't you kill them for me?
- Wifey, just watch.

05:38.600 --> 05:40.400
- I'll do it for you.
- Great!

05:45.640 --> 05:48.280
Weiwei, you go to school
in Capital City, right?

05:57.400 --> 05:58.600
I'm in Capital City, too.

05:58.680 --> 06:00.360
Should we meet in person?

06:00.440 --> 06:01.800
I'll take you out to eat.

06:01.880 --> 06:04.080
I know a good Japanese restaurant

06:04.160 --> 06:06.440
as good as those in Japan
with three Michelin stars.

06:06.680 --> 06:07.880
That's okay.

06:07.960 --> 06:10.120
We'll just have our fun in the game.

06:12.440 --> 06:13.880
There's a saying nowadays,

06:13.960 --> 06:16.920
that you never know
who's on the other side of the screen.

06:17.000 --> 06:18.600
I just want to make sure.

06:18.880 --> 06:21.400
I want to see what you look like.

06:21.480 --> 06:23.960
Will you show me a photo?

06:40.600 --> 06:43.200
Professor Yu's class is incredible!

06:43.560 --> 06:44.400
- Hi.
- Hi.

06:44.480 --> 06:45.920
Hello.

06:48.760 --> 06:50.920
Weiwei, it's all clear. Hurry!

06:51.440 --> 06:54.280
What's wrong? Why did the power go out?

06:55.680 --> 06:56.760
I think the fuse is blown.

06:58.160 --> 07:01.040
I was only making noodles,
and the fuse is blown?

07:01.400 --> 07:02.960
Will we get in trouble?

07:03.320 --> 07:05.080
Girl, before you cook anything,

07:05.160 --> 07:07.080
won't you calculate
the flow of electricity first?

07:07.160 --> 07:08.040
Come on, girl!

07:08.520 --> 07:11.760
I'm a computer major,
not a double-E major!

07:11.840 --> 07:14.280
What now? My noodles are still raw!

07:14.720 --> 07:17.640
What do you think?
Give me half of your noodles!

07:21.680 --> 07:22.680
All done.

07:23.360 --> 07:24.560
Remarkable!

07:30.200 --> 07:31.920
No wonder girls, like us,

07:32.000 --> 07:34.000
in the S&E department
have trouble finding love.

07:34.080 --> 07:35.760
We do our own handy work.

07:35.840 --> 07:37.800
What do we need boys for?

07:38.720 --> 07:40.440
First of all, I did the handy work,

07:40.520 --> 07:42.840
but it has nothing to do
with the fact that you're still single.

07:42.920 --> 07:44.560
Second of all, Ms. Erxi,

07:44.640 --> 07:47.800
my gaming friend was asking for my photos,
but I suddenly went offline!

07:47.880 --> 07:49.720
He must think I'm evading him!

07:49.800 --> 07:53.040
Tell me, how will you compensate
the damage to my reputation?

07:54.840 --> 07:57.560
Is it Zhenshui Wuxiang,
your spouse in online game?

07:58.000 --> 07:59.680
Nice, Weiwei!

07:59.880 --> 08:00.840
Stop.

08:01.480 --> 08:03.320
How do you know all that?

08:03.880 --> 08:05.360
Have you been spying on me again?

08:07.840 --> 08:10.240
Don't get bogged down by details.

08:11.600 --> 08:13.960
Will you send him your photo?

08:14.040 --> 08:15.320
Of course not.

08:15.520 --> 08:18.400
We only became in-game spouses
for the territory quest.

08:18.600 --> 08:20.920
It's weird to send him photos,

08:21.000 --> 08:23.200
but it's bad to just go offline, too.

08:23.280 --> 08:25.400
I should at least find an excuse,

08:25.480 --> 08:27.200
like my laptop's busted,

08:27.280 --> 08:28.840
and all my photos are gone.

08:34.159 --> 08:35.280
No way!

08:38.159 --> 08:40.799
Your laptop's busted?
All the photos are gone?

08:41.720 --> 08:43.280
You jinxed it!

08:44.800 --> 08:46.640
How can this be?

08:47.000 --> 08:49.720
Weiwei, I forgot to tell you,

08:49.800 --> 08:51.680
when I borrowed your laptop yesterday,

08:51.760 --> 08:55.240
I accidentally dropped the laptop.

08:56.240 --> 08:57.960
Where do you think you're going?

08:58.040 --> 08:59.200
Get back here! Come here!

08:59.280 --> 09:00.560
- I'm sorry!
- What happened?

09:00.640 --> 09:01.920
- Explain yourself!
- I'm sorry.

09:04.280 --> 09:05.280
Let's go!

09:05.360 --> 09:07.640
At least let me finish my noodles!

09:07.720 --> 09:08.800
What noodles?

09:08.880 --> 09:10.640
You broke my laptop,
and you still want to eat?

09:10.720 --> 09:11.680
I don't think so! Let's go!

09:15.960 --> 09:17.800
It's such a beautiful day.

09:17.880 --> 09:21.320
Xiaoling is with her boyfriend,
Sisi is at a class reunion party,

09:21.400 --> 09:23.520
yet I have to accompany you
to fix your laptop.

09:23.600 --> 09:25.960
This beautiful day is totally wasted.

09:26.040 --> 09:27.080
How dare you say that?

09:27.160 --> 09:29.240
Who broke my laptop? Come on!

09:33.200 --> 09:34.240
Here.

09:47.320 --> 09:49.760
There are new movies out.

09:49.840 --> 09:51.720
After we drop off the laptop,

09:51.800 --> 09:53.520
let's go catch some movies.

09:53.680 --> 09:54.840
I'm not dropping it off.

09:54.920 --> 09:57.600
I'll change out the motherboard myself.
It's cheaper and faster.

09:57.680 --> 09:59.680
Anyway, I need to use my laptop tonight.

09:59.760 --> 10:01.720
What's the hurry?

10:01.800 --> 10:05.800
A hard-working and ambitious
computer major like myself

10:05.880 --> 10:08.920
cannot be without a computer,
even for a day. Okay?

10:09.000 --> 10:10.880
Yeah, right! What's really going on?

10:14.360 --> 10:15.400
I have a duel date.

10:16.680 --> 10:18.560
I knew it!

10:23.960 --> 10:26.040
Time flies! We're sophomores now.

10:26.280 --> 10:27.680
At Qing University,

10:27.760 --> 10:30.480
men overwhelmingly outnumber women,

10:30.560 --> 10:32.880
especially the Computer Department.

10:32.960 --> 10:36.800
I never thought, after two years,
I would still be single. It's so pathetic.

10:37.720 --> 10:40.720
You didn't pick this place
precisely for that reason?

10:43.600 --> 10:46.080
Well, not entirely, of course.

10:46.920 --> 10:49.240
Qing's Computer Department
is ranked number one in the nation.

10:49.320 --> 10:51.360
It's always been my dream college.

10:51.440 --> 10:53.440
Computing is also the subject that I love.

10:53.840 --> 10:55.640
But even with all these,

10:55.720 --> 10:58.080
I could still consider my happiness.

11:02.960 --> 11:04.640
Let's go check it out!

11:15.400 --> 11:16.560
What's going on?

11:18.440 --> 11:21.840
CAMPUS BASKETBALL CHAMPIONSHIP

11:27.760 --> 11:29.560
COMPUTER DEPT. VS. BIOLOGY DEPT.

11:32.640 --> 11:35.160
Lord Xiao Nai is returning
to the basketball court!

11:35.680 --> 11:38.280
That's great! We can see him play again!

11:38.600 --> 11:40.120
Computer Department
versus Biology Department.

11:40.200 --> 11:42.760
Xiao Nai's the key player.
Surely we'll see him this time?

11:42.840 --> 11:45.040
Not necessarily. He's a senior now.

11:45.120 --> 11:46.640
He's rarely on campus.

11:47.240 --> 11:51.000
I hear the mystery forum
hasn't been updated at all.

11:51.080 --> 11:53.160
I reckon
this is just another publicity stunt.

11:53.640 --> 11:56.080
Who cares?
Checking it out won't cost anything.

11:56.160 --> 11:58.880
Anyway, it's the last chance
to see him in person.

11:58.960 --> 12:01.560
That's true.
It pains me to think about it.

12:01.640 --> 12:02.680
Why doesn't he go to graduate school?

12:02.760 --> 12:05.400
- Right? What a shame.
- So true.

12:05.480 --> 12:07.120
Everyone from your dorm has to go!

12:07.200 --> 12:09.360
We have to grab the seats
an hour ahead of time.

12:10.920 --> 12:12.840
Weiwei, I had no idea!

12:12.920 --> 12:14.600
You're an admirer, too?

12:14.680 --> 12:16.840
Of course! He's Lord Xiao Nai!

12:16.920 --> 12:19.600
I've downloaded
all the software he's released.

12:19.800 --> 12:23.000
If there's player ranking at school,
like they have in e-sports,

12:23.080 --> 12:26.320
he would definitely be number one
on all fronts.

12:27.520 --> 12:29.760
Girl, you're so deep.

12:29.840 --> 12:32.080
I only care for the face and the body.

12:32.440 --> 12:35.080
I don't have the brains of a genius
like you.

12:35.720 --> 12:36.960
By the way,

12:37.040 --> 12:39.800
who blacked out
that video of him swimming?

12:39.880 --> 12:43.080
I really want to see it!

12:44.760 --> 12:45.680
Let's go.

13:00.680 --> 13:04.080
Yiran, let's buy this thing.

13:04.280 --> 13:07.480
Nana, I don't even know him.

13:07.560 --> 13:09.320
How can I ask for his help?

13:09.400 --> 13:13.720
Don't you worry! A couple of days ago,
I befriended a guy from their dorm.

13:13.800 --> 13:15.720
So, I came up with this idea.

13:15.800 --> 13:20.000
We'll buy a RAM stick and go ask for help.

13:20.400 --> 13:22.480
As soon as he hears your name,

13:22.560 --> 13:25.960
I'm sure he'll be eager to help you.
Don't stress!

13:28.960 --> 13:31.720
I told him the shipment is on its way.

13:32.120 --> 13:34.200
Just have him sign for it, okay?

13:36.040 --> 13:38.520
Hi, how much is this?

13:38.600 --> 13:39.560
500.

13:39.920 --> 13:43.160
500? That's so expensive!

13:44.040 --> 13:46.040
Go ask around. It's the same everywhere.

13:46.280 --> 13:47.480
You get what you pay for, okay?

13:48.360 --> 13:50.160
Will you give us a discount? 450?

13:50.680 --> 13:53.520
Not a cent lower.
This is already the cut-rate price.

13:55.360 --> 13:56.360
Mister,

13:56.680 --> 13:59.400
isn't your price a bit unreasonable?

14:00.560 --> 14:03.720
The gold contact's glisten
of your RAM stick is totally off.

14:03.800 --> 14:05.160
It's obviously used.

14:05.240 --> 14:08.080
You're selling it as if it's brand new,
at double the price.

14:08.160 --> 14:09.120
Isn't that cheating the customer?

14:09.200 --> 14:12.400
No way! What do you know?
Don't be a busybody, okay?

14:13.640 --> 14:15.440
I'm a computer major.
I know what I'm talking about.

14:16.240 --> 14:19.480
Your shop is right by the campus,
yet you're cheating students.

14:19.920 --> 14:22.560
Won't it hurt your business
if word gets out?

14:22.680 --> 14:25.480
Right? You're so dishonest!

14:26.160 --> 14:30.280
Where's the old shopkeeper? Huh?
Is there a new owner now?

14:31.720 --> 14:34.360
What old shopkeeper? It's always been me.

14:34.520 --> 14:36.200
What's the matter with you girls?

14:36.280 --> 14:37.960
Do you have some beef with me?

14:38.600 --> 14:40.840
You're decent-looking.
Why are you being nasty?

14:40.920 --> 14:42.240
Get lost.

14:42.320 --> 14:45.480
Hey, this brand of RAM sticks
go for less than 300.

14:45.560 --> 14:47.000
You can search online
if you don't believe me.

14:49.240 --> 14:52.520
Online shops sell fake stuff.
That's why it's so cheap.

14:52.840 --> 14:54.560
I think that's Bei Weiwei.

14:57.520 --> 15:00.960
Thank you, Miss.
I don't think the owner would cheat me.

15:01.280 --> 15:02.800
He's running a shop.

15:02.880 --> 15:04.480
There's no harm
in letting him earn some money.

15:13.520 --> 15:17.520
Who's she trying to impress
with that pompous yet compassionate act?

15:17.600 --> 15:21.240
We're the bad guys
for trying to help her? Here.

15:22.320 --> 15:23.400
I know!

15:23.480 --> 15:26.360
It must be because you're Bei Weiwei
and she's Meng Yiran.

15:27.320 --> 15:30.320
Meng Yiran.
Don't tell me you don't know her?

15:30.440 --> 15:31.920
She's the campus beauty.

15:34.760 --> 15:36.200
I thought she looked familiar.

15:36.280 --> 15:38.840
That must be the reason why!

15:38.920 --> 15:43.800
The two of you were neck-to-neck
at last year's campus beauty contest.

15:43.880 --> 15:45.960
You can't blame her
for being hostile toward you.

15:46.040 --> 15:47.720
It was not neck-to-neck!

15:47.800 --> 15:50.440
Who sent in my photo last year?

15:52.480 --> 15:55.400
You already checked my laptop
and cell phone last year.

15:55.480 --> 15:56.600
It wasn't me.

15:58.000 --> 16:01.840
Anyway, why would I use a blurry photo
like that?

16:01.920 --> 16:03.400
If I took the photo,

16:03.480 --> 16:07.040
it'd be high definition, front-view,

16:07.200 --> 16:09.080
and of you coming out of the shower.

16:10.320 --> 16:13.600
By the way, do you think
Meng Yiran's photo was retouched?

16:13.680 --> 16:15.760
She must have spent days photoshopping.

16:15.840 --> 16:18.520
She's nowhere near as pretty
as the online photo.

16:18.600 --> 16:20.280
If her photo was sans retouch,

16:20.360 --> 16:23.040
you would never have lost
last year, Weiwei.

16:25.640 --> 16:27.720
I'm going to the internet cafe later.

16:27.800 --> 16:30.880
Also, I remember
she won the contest last year.

16:30.960 --> 16:34.960
She came in first, and I second.
It should be me being hostile towards her.

16:35.040 --> 16:36.760
Why is she hostile towards me?

16:36.840 --> 16:38.360
Who knows?

16:38.880 --> 16:43.040
Maybe she's flat-chested?

16:43.720 --> 16:45.160
Get lost!

16:46.720 --> 16:47.960
She must be!

16:49.080 --> 16:51.360
Now I know why you have trouble
landing a boyfriend.

16:52.000 --> 16:53.920
Why? Tell me! I'll change!

16:54.720 --> 16:57.600
Because you pay more attention to girls!

16:57.680 --> 17:00.160
- Weiwei, don't make me hurt you!
- Fine. I'll stop.

17:00.560 --> 17:02.200
Take my laptop back. Bye!

17:04.839 --> 17:08.359
Me, single? You're the one
who's always on the computer.

17:15.640 --> 17:19.160
Your dad told me
you plan to start your own company?

17:20.760 --> 17:22.200
That is the plan.

17:28.160 --> 17:29.320
Doing what?

17:29.960 --> 17:31.520
The initial plan is to develop two games.

17:31.880 --> 17:35.560
If you win this game,
I'll give you a gift.

18:00.880 --> 18:01.880
Weiwei!

18:02.760 --> 18:04.880
Luwei Weiwei,
I thought you were afraid to come.

18:06.120 --> 18:07.160
I don't think I'm late.

18:08.000 --> 18:10.960
Late or not, you're still going down.
Prepare to hand over the necklace.

18:12.440 --> 18:13.280
Let's begin.

18:16.880 --> 18:17.720
It's your turn.

19:23.600 --> 19:24.440
Good game.

19:28.360 --> 19:29.200
Good game.

19:29.920 --> 19:31.040
Crap!

19:31.120 --> 19:33.720
No wonder Luwei Weiwei is
the only female player ranked for dueling.

19:33.800 --> 19:36.560
- She's playing him for sport!
- Right?

19:36.840 --> 19:39.240
How is she so good
at the "walk-on-air" trick?

19:39.520 --> 19:41.360
That dodge was incredible!

19:41.440 --> 19:44.280
She only places sixth
with that kind of skill?

19:44.600 --> 19:45.840
I wonder who's number one?

19:45.920 --> 19:48.760
Is number one the legendary Yixiao Naihe?

19:48.840 --> 19:51.600
I've never met him.
The name is pretentious enough!

19:51.680 --> 19:54.360
How did he come up
with that avatar handle?

19:54.800 --> 19:57.120
Luwei Weiwei, let's go again.

19:59.080 --> 20:02.480
Sure, but I'm at an internet cafe.

20:02.560 --> 20:05.800
I only paid for an hour's time.
Let's get it over with.

20:07.040 --> 20:09.280
Per our earlier agreement,

20:09.400 --> 20:12.920
you won this game,
so Uncle will give you a gift.

20:14.480 --> 20:16.600
I'll gift you this place.

20:16.800 --> 20:19.080
Aren't you going to start
a gaming company?

20:19.160 --> 20:22.240
With remodeling,
this place will be enough for the start.

20:23.320 --> 20:27.040
Uncle, that's your offer.
I didn't agree to it.

20:27.680 --> 20:29.840
- You don't want it?
- No.

20:33.160 --> 20:34.960
Good boy! You're quite ambitious!

20:36.320 --> 20:40.200
I just think it's more fun
to start from nothing.

20:41.240 --> 20:44.200
Plus, I already found the spot.

20:52.680 --> 20:56.360
We're both genetic mutations
because we're into computers.

20:57.320 --> 21:01.080
Your dad is an archaeologist
and your mom is a historian,

21:01.160 --> 21:03.080
yet you're into computers.

21:03.160 --> 21:05.960
I can see that you're just like me.

21:06.480 --> 21:09.440
I don't have the energy
to run this place anymore.

21:09.520 --> 21:12.680
If you don't want it, I'll shut it down.

21:12.880 --> 21:14.600
- Sir, you have a call.
- Okay.

22:28.560 --> 22:29.600
What's up?

22:30.720 --> 22:33.480
It's about time.
Let's go have dinner at your place.

22:33.560 --> 22:35.280
I'll make a couple of dishes for you.

23:00.840 --> 23:05.000
Xiaoling.

23:05.080 --> 23:06.880
Stop! What now?

23:06.960 --> 23:08.640
I don't know how to do this.

23:09.560 --> 23:12.200
Erxi, go get the bedding for me!

23:12.280 --> 23:13.560
I'm busy.

23:16.160 --> 23:18.360
- This and this.
- Which one?

23:19.640 --> 23:22.480
Hurry. It's going to rain!

23:24.320 --> 23:25.320
Come on.

23:31.200 --> 23:33.880
Erxi, will you go get the bedding for me?

23:33.960 --> 23:36.040
You have time to nag at me.
You can go get them yourself.

23:36.120 --> 23:38.120
- I have a facial mask on!
- Sisi.

23:38.200 --> 23:39.480
- Someone's knocking.
- Open up, Erxi!

23:39.560 --> 23:42.240
- So annoying! Coming!
- Hurry, Xiaoling.

23:42.800 --> 23:45.760
Oh, no! Thank you, Weiwei! Thanks.

23:45.840 --> 23:48.800
It's pouring outside!
Why didn't you get the bedding?

23:57.600 --> 24:00.760
Weiwei, why are you so late?
Where were you?

24:00.840 --> 24:01.840
Where else?

24:01.920 --> 24:03.920
Ms. Bei must have been battling
in her online game.

24:04.000 --> 24:05.760
I had to bring back her laptop!

24:05.840 --> 24:07.680
By the way, I've put it back.

24:08.480 --> 24:09.960
Thanks, Ms. Erxi.

24:11.680 --> 24:15.480
Speaking of which,
Ms. Bei and I intervened an injustice,

24:15.560 --> 24:17.800
- but we got so mad in the end!
- What happened?

24:17.880 --> 24:19.640
It's Meng Yiran!

24:19.800 --> 24:21.160
Meng Yiran?

24:22.240 --> 24:26.440
Weiwei, you know Meng Yiran?
How come you never mentioned it?

24:27.080 --> 24:28.200
I don't know her.

24:28.280 --> 24:33.120
Erxi and I went to get a computer part,
and we saw the owner trying to cheat her.

24:33.200 --> 24:35.560
He sold a RAM stick at double price.

24:35.640 --> 24:38.160
As a computer major,
how can I keep my mouth shut?

24:38.240 --> 24:41.520
You helped her, but what did she say?

24:42.400 --> 24:47.480
"Thank you, Miss.
I don't think the owner would cheat me.

24:47.560 --> 24:49.640
He's running a shop.

24:49.720 --> 24:52.000
There's no harm
in letting him earn some money."

24:52.280 --> 24:54.000
She's so generous? What about us?

24:54.200 --> 24:59.240
She made us seem so petty and philistine.
In the end, the owner kicked us out!

24:59.320 --> 25:02.440
Weiwei, what will you do
with your laptop?

25:02.560 --> 25:04.880
Changing the motherboard is costly.
I thought about it.

25:04.960 --> 25:08.480
I'll just buy a new capacitor online
and switch it out.

25:11.080 --> 25:12.680
Capacitor?

25:13.720 --> 25:16.440
I'm a computer major, too,

25:16.520 --> 25:21.160
yet somehow I don't think I'm studying
the same thing as Ms. Bei Weiwei.

25:22.560 --> 25:25.400
- I don't get it at all.
- Me neither.

25:27.600 --> 25:31.560
I'm so isolated, lonesome, and cold.

25:35.480 --> 25:37.640
Where's the stuff I left here
this morning? Has anyone seen it?

25:38.520 --> 25:42.000
- Are you looking for the gaming notebook?
- You know where it is?

25:42.360 --> 25:44.960
- Right here.
- Thanks! Kiss!

25:46.200 --> 25:49.560
You say you take notes every day.
Heaven knows what you're doing?

25:49.640 --> 25:52.800
Can't there be anything else in your life
besides studying, playing online games,

25:52.880 --> 25:54.520
and taking notes?

25:54.600 --> 25:56.960
I don't need anything else.
I'm content this way.

25:57.040 --> 25:58.240
Don't you underestimate it.

25:58.320 --> 26:02.040
This notebook might help me
become a game designer.

26:02.120 --> 26:04.240
With luck, I'll join Fengteng Technology,

26:04.320 --> 26:06.760
or maybe work on
"A Chinese Ghost Story Online Game."

26:06.840 --> 26:08.200
Erxi!

26:08.680 --> 26:12.480
I don't get it at all.
Others play online games to kill time.

26:12.560 --> 26:14.520
You plan your life around online games.

26:15.120 --> 26:18.480
Top student's brains are truly different
from our normal brains.

26:33.960 --> 26:35.800
Yiran, I have to write my article.

26:35.880 --> 26:38.280
Wait here. I'll be done in a bit.

26:46.840 --> 26:50.280
Bei Weiwei is the one who helped us
haggle prices yesterday?

26:50.360 --> 26:53.040
Yes, runner-up
of the campus beauty contest.

26:53.120 --> 26:54.480
She's the one who lost to you.

26:55.280 --> 26:58.360
- She's quite pretty.
- Not nearly as pretty as you!

26:58.840 --> 27:03.400
She's the conventional-looking type.
There's nothing special about her.

27:03.480 --> 27:06.520
If she was in a TV show,
she'd be the supporting role.

27:06.600 --> 27:08.280
She's not nearly as elegant as you.

27:08.720 --> 27:11.240
Nana, don't say that about her.

27:11.360 --> 27:14.000
Fine. I'm sorry for telling the truth.

27:15.160 --> 27:18.640
Contrary to what I'd imagined,
she's very friendly.

27:19.840 --> 27:23.080
Yiran, don't be so easily fooled by her.

27:23.160 --> 27:26.200
She was just showing off
that she knows more, and we're dumb.

27:27.680 --> 27:28.800
Would she really do that?

27:30.600 --> 27:34.880
Ms. Yiran, just because you're in love
with a computer major,

27:35.160 --> 27:39.160
it doesn't mean
all computer majors are good people.

27:39.400 --> 27:41.880
- That's nonsense!
- It's true.

27:42.160 --> 27:44.080
The other day, Cao Guang snapped a photo

27:44.160 --> 27:45.920
of Bei Weiwei getting out
of a luxury car.

27:46.400 --> 27:48.520
That car must have cost millions!

27:49.160 --> 27:51.160
Bei Weiwei isn't as innocent
as you think.

27:51.800 --> 27:53.760
- Really?
- Of course!

27:54.760 --> 27:56.560
Speak of the devil.

27:59.080 --> 28:03.640
Cao Guang, show me and Yiran
the photo you took of Bei Weiwei

28:03.720 --> 28:04.680
getting out of that luxury car.

28:05.440 --> 28:06.280
How did you know that?

28:08.040 --> 28:10.440
I was right behind you.

28:10.520 --> 28:12.960
You were fast.
I didn't even think to snap a photo.

28:13.640 --> 28:16.080
- I deleted it.
- What?

28:16.960 --> 28:20.040
Are you into her? Are you protecting her?

28:22.120 --> 28:24.520
Are you kidding?
Why would I go for a girl like that?

28:29.840 --> 28:32.480
Did you hear what Cao Guang said, Yiran?

28:32.600 --> 28:36.240
Looks can be deceiving. Don't be so naive.

28:58.360 --> 29:01.200
Weiwei, Zhenyi Tech is looking
for summer interns, too.

29:01.280 --> 29:03.280
They want computer majors.
Should I sign you up?

29:04.440 --> 29:06.560
Sure! Sounds good.

29:06.640 --> 29:09.400
We need to get a summer internship anyway.

29:10.120 --> 29:12.040
Why don't you sign up
for Xiaoling and Sisi, too?

29:12.360 --> 29:13.880
Okay!

29:26.560 --> 29:27.720
Got it!

29:30.080 --> 29:32.600
You fixed it, for real?

29:32.680 --> 29:35.840
I'll depend on you
for all my computer hardware woes.

29:35.920 --> 29:38.680
No problem. It's a piece of cake.
I'll be at your service.

29:39.720 --> 29:41.640
Back to gaming
as soon as the laptop is fixed?

29:41.720 --> 29:43.880
Gaming is like your life!

29:45.200 --> 29:48.760
I'm done with studying.
I'm done with all my work.

29:49.480 --> 29:53.080
This just goes to show how efficient I am.

29:53.560 --> 29:57.760
Please! That was just a random comment,
and you get all narcissistic.

29:59.040 --> 30:02.520
I used to think playing games
is a waste of time, too.

30:02.600 --> 30:04.480
I only found out, after I tried it,

30:04.560 --> 30:06.360
that it's a fantastic world.

30:07.320 --> 30:10.680
I've got the dream and the talent.
Why not work hard for it?

30:51.880 --> 30:55.400
Weiwei, meet me at the Rock of Lives.
Let's annul our in-game marriage.

30:56.200 --> 30:57.040
Why?

30:57.840 --> 31:00.000
Sorry, please don't ask.

31:00.080 --> 31:02.840
I'll give you a set of OP equipment
as compensation.

31:03.040 --> 31:04.520
There's a breakup fee?

31:07.400 --> 31:10.600
It's okay. I'll be right over. See you.

31:30.760 --> 31:33.880
You came, Weiwei. I'm really sorry.

31:34.840 --> 31:37.080
It's fine. Let's go.

31:37.160 --> 31:39.160
ROCK OF LIVES

31:48.600 --> 31:52.400
What's tonight? The moon remains the same.
When will love and hatred ever end?

31:52.480 --> 31:57.120
Across lands, seas, and lunar phases,
happiness is the most elusive of all.

31:57.240 --> 31:58.680
ANNUL IN-GAME MARRIAGE?

31:58.760 --> 32:00.120
YES

32:18.000 --> 32:21.480
Drink the water of amnesia,
and partners become strangers.

32:28.040 --> 32:30.720
Luwei Weiwei and Zhenshui Wuxiang
have fallen out of love.

32:30.800 --> 32:33.760
Your time with each other ends here,
as well as your relationship.

32:34.680 --> 32:37.880
- I've got things to do. See you.
- Wait.

32:42.360 --> 32:46.200
Please accept this equipment,
as my compensation to you.

32:46.560 --> 32:50.840
It's fine, really. We only became
in-game spouses for a quest.

32:51.120 --> 32:52.520
There are no hard feelings
for breaking up.

32:55.520 --> 32:56.880
I should go for my daily quests.

32:57.120 --> 32:58.920
We'll take on monsters
together again sometime.

32:59.840 --> 33:00.680
All right.

33:06.720 --> 33:11.320
Weiwei, why are you here collecting herbs?

33:11.840 --> 33:12.840
What's wrong?

33:12.920 --> 33:14.960
What's wrong?
Did you break up with Zhenshui?

33:16.280 --> 33:19.360
Yes. I thought you have big news.

33:19.640 --> 33:21.360
Why are you so calm?

33:21.440 --> 33:24.600
I hear he and Xiaoyu Yaoyao
will soon become in-game spouses.

33:24.680 --> 33:25.520
Xiaoyu Yaoyao?

33:26.280 --> 33:27.520
Don't you know her?

33:27.720 --> 33:29.840
She won the Dreamy Angel contest,

33:29.920 --> 33:31.680
known as the number one beauty
of "A Chinese Ghost Story Online Game."

33:32.720 --> 33:35.000
Drop the herbs and check out the site.

33:35.080 --> 33:36.000
I'll go right now.

33:42.560 --> 33:43.560
DREAMY ANGEL CONTEST

33:44.200 --> 33:46.680
WINNER: XIAOYU YAOYAO

33:49.920 --> 33:50.760
You broke up for real?

33:54.640 --> 33:57.560
We only became in-game spouses
for the quest.

33:57.640 --> 33:58.680
Don't take it to heart.

33:59.880 --> 34:01.520
It's still a shame.

34:01.840 --> 34:03.640
Zhenshui is a nice guy.

34:04.440 --> 34:06.640
I didn't think
he'd be infatuated with beauty.

34:06.720 --> 34:09.560
On the other hand,
Xiaoyu Yaoyao is really pretty.

34:10.159 --> 34:14.280
I heard she fancied that guy
on the equipment ranking.

34:14.360 --> 34:16.679
I didn't expect her to be with Zhenshui.

34:16.880 --> 34:20.199
But I did notice
that they've been leveling together.

34:21.440 --> 34:23.000
I see.

34:25.480 --> 34:29.960
It's not all Zhenshui's fault, though.
The thing is, Weiwei...

34:32.639 --> 34:33.840
What?

34:34.760 --> 34:38.719
You're so skilled.
You're number six on the duel ranking.

34:38.800 --> 34:42.280
You never ask the boys for equipment,
and you never post photos of yourself.

34:42.360 --> 34:46.840
The thing is, everyone suspects
that you're a bio-guy in disguise.

34:48.080 --> 34:49.360
Bio-guy in disguise?

34:52.520 --> 34:55.480
What? I'm a bio-guy in disguise
because I don't post photos?

34:56.199 --> 34:57.960
What's with this superficial world?

34:58.960 --> 35:01.800
Bei Weiwei, you're the prettiest girl
in our department.

35:01.880 --> 35:03.960
If you say that,
what will the rest of us do?

35:04.040 --> 35:07.000
Be quiet!
I'm in the middle of that web fiction.

35:07.080 --> 35:10.520
I was so wrapped up in it,
when you snapped me back to reality!

35:14.040 --> 35:17.560
Congratulations to Mr. Zhenshui Wuxiang
and Ms. Xiaoyu Yaoyao.

35:17.640 --> 35:20.960
May your merry matrimony last forever,
and never shall you part.

35:46.360 --> 35:48.080
Nice!

35:50.840 --> 35:52.680
- I think they'll go far.
- Exactly! Nice!

35:52.760 --> 35:54.560
- They're quite compatible.
- Right?

35:54.640 --> 35:57.160
They're a match made in heaven!

36:03.360 --> 36:04.560
That's true.

36:05.000 --> 36:06.480
Definitely.

36:11.120 --> 36:14.280
XIAOYU QINGQING, XIAOYU FEIFEI
XIAOYU MIANMIAN

36:21.600 --> 36:24.920
How much red envelop money do you think
Zhenshui Wuxiang will give out this time?

36:25.000 --> 36:28.320
888, it's a good omen. I only want 888.

36:29.280 --> 36:31.440
I can't help but think of Luwei Weiwei.

36:31.520 --> 36:34.120
I wonder how she's feeling now?

36:34.960 --> 36:36.040
Luwei Weiwei?

36:37.200 --> 36:38.560
Isn't that Luwei Weiwei?

36:38.800 --> 36:40.040
Do you see her?

36:40.120 --> 36:43.520
I see Zhenshui Wuxiang's former
in-game spouse on Red Sparrow Bridge.

36:43.600 --> 36:45.960
- That's right. I see her.
- Really?

36:46.040 --> 36:49.760
There she is! She looks so sad!

36:49.840 --> 36:52.480
Attention is only ever given to newlyweds.

36:52.560 --> 36:55.080
No one cares about the jilted lover.

36:55.160 --> 36:59.200
Darn! This is going to be a good show!
She might be here to storm the wedding.

37:19.960 --> 37:22.240
Textspeak again?

37:22.320 --> 37:24.400
- I hate textspeak!
- Hurry, Weiwei! I need to go, too!

37:24.480 --> 37:26.480
What's wrong with textspeak?
That's discrimination!

37:26.560 --> 37:27.560
Hold on!

37:28.360 --> 37:30.040
I'm for Luwei Weiwei
stealing Zhenshui back!

37:30.120 --> 37:32.280
- Xiaoyu Yaoyao is mine!
- Hurry!

37:35.760 --> 37:37.400
Okay! Be right out!

37:41.760 --> 37:44.200
Love triangle? Why? She's beautiful, too.

37:44.280 --> 37:46.320
Why is she so brazen?

37:46.400 --> 37:48.880
She stole her man.
Of course, she's showing off!

37:48.960 --> 37:51.440
Xiaoyu Yaoyao is shameless.

37:51.520 --> 37:53.160
Totally shameless!

37:54.440 --> 37:59.160
"Shameless" is an attack. Player is banned
from commenting for 24 hours.

38:03.920 --> 38:05.600
What's with Luwei Weiwei?

38:05.680 --> 38:07.880
She got dumped!
How dare she storm the wedding?

38:08.200 --> 38:10.440
Zhenshui, what's with you?

38:10.520 --> 38:13.320
That hag must be jealous of Yaoyao.
She's here to stir up trouble.

38:13.800 --> 38:15.320
Yaoyao is being trampled on!

38:15.520 --> 38:18.120
- You must take proper action!
- That's right! You owe it to us.

38:19.040 --> 38:22.080
Don't blame Zhenshui.
I'm sure he doesn't want this, either.

38:26.280 --> 38:28.520
Yaoyao, I'll do right by you.

38:31.120 --> 38:31.960
Giddy-up.

38:36.320 --> 38:37.840
Hurry, Weiwei!

38:58.720 --> 39:00.760
I only went to the bathroom.

39:00.840 --> 39:04.960
What have I done?
Everyone thinks I'm storming the wedding.

39:12.200 --> 39:14.200
If I run away now,

39:14.560 --> 39:18.280
the gossipy crowd would think
that I'm heartbroken.

39:27.320 --> 39:30.600
What's wrong?
Didn't you say no hard feelings yesterday?

39:30.680 --> 39:34.120
I offered you compensation, too,
but you rejected it.

39:35.240 --> 39:38.280
Dude, I'm only here as an onlooker.

39:44.360 --> 39:47.160
I can't leave, yet I can't stay.

39:51.640 --> 39:52.600
Got it!

39:59.600 --> 40:00.560
HERBS ON SALE

40:00.640 --> 40:02.240
Come on! Take a look!

40:02.320 --> 40:04.200
Fully certified herbalist
with the latest medicine.

40:04.280 --> 40:06.200
- 20 percent off the regular price!
- She's selling medicine?

40:06.280 --> 40:07.840
Fully certified medicine!

40:07.920 --> 40:09.640
- Giddy-up.
- 20 percent off? That's cheap!

40:09.720 --> 40:10.960
Nice deal! I want some.

40:11.040 --> 40:13.080
- I want some.
- Me, too.

40:13.160 --> 40:14.960
- I'll take some.
- I got here first.

40:15.040 --> 40:17.440
- Give it.
- I got here first. Don't push!

40:17.520 --> 40:19.120
Be orderly and form a line.

40:20.280 --> 40:21.160
Don't skip me.

40:21.240 --> 40:22.800
I want some. Give it!

40:23.800 --> 40:24.960
I got here first.

40:25.040 --> 40:27.520
All right. I'm all sold out.

40:27.960 --> 40:28.920
When will you be here again?

40:29.000 --> 40:29.840
- When?
- Right?

40:29.920 --> 40:31.760
- When will you sell medicine again?
- When?

40:32.600 --> 40:34.000
It depends on my mood.

40:34.840 --> 40:36.880
- Let's go.
- Come on.

40:36.960 --> 40:39.160
- Let's get out of here.
- Let's go.

40:39.240 --> 40:40.600
Go on.

40:41.240 --> 40:42.400
Luwei Weiwei!

41:05.520 --> 41:07.000
Yixiao Naihe?

41:08.920 --> 41:12.040
The server's number one player,
Yixiao Naihe?

41:16.800 --> 41:18.920
A lord! An idol! A rich guy!

41:25.040 --> 41:26.920
Yes, Mr. Yixiao Naihe?

41:28.640 --> 41:29.840
What do you think of the wedding?

41:32.080 --> 41:34.480
Did he come to gossip, too?

41:35.680 --> 41:36.520
It's grand.

41:37.240 --> 41:39.520
Would you like an even grander wedding?

41:44.280 --> 41:45.240
Form an in-game marriage with me.

44:16.800 --> 44:19.240
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
